This paper is likely to belong to the Multimedia (cs.MM) category as it deals with online video streaming. It may also belong to the Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) category as it discusses bandwidth consumption and server bandwidth. Additionally, it could be categorized under Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) as it analyzes user behavior. Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC) could also be a possible category as it deals with optimizing server bandwidth usage. Finally, Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC) could be a relevant category as the paper aims to improve user QoE.
